---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Garden — Our Story, Philosophy & People — Tango Garden"
  description="The story behind Tango Garden Cologne — who we are, why we do this, and what we believe."
  canonical="https://tangogarden.de/pages/the-garden"
>
  <Fragment set:html={`
<!-- Hero -->
<section class="garden-hero">
  <div class="garden-hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="garden-hero-content">
    <h1>This Is Your Garden</h1>
    <div class="garden-scroll-hint">
      <p>Discover Our Story</p>
      <span class="garden-scroll-arrow">↓</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Story -->
<section class="garden-story" id="our-story">
  <div class="garden-story-inner">
    <div class="garden-story-text">
      <div class="garden-story-eyebrow">Where This Began</div>
      <p>Hi! My name's Vangelis and I was born in Crete, Greece, where my favourite season was always summer. Every evening, our small garden would fill with the scent of night-bloom jasmine. It wasn't much — a few chairs, a plastic table — but it was a place where people came together. My uncles would drop by unannounced; friends, neighbours, strangers would sit, eat, laugh, argue, and share stories and silence.</p>
      <p>That garden was my first lesson in connection — a simple, living space that brought people closer and helped us catch our breath from the noise of life.</p>
      <p>Every evening, people would gather. Not because they were invited. Not because there was an event. But because the garden <em>existed</em> — a shared space where showing up meant you belonged.</p>
      <p>They shared food and told stories. They argued about politics and taught the children old songs. Conversations were always loud. And on celebrations, someone was always dancing.</p>
      <p>What struck me wasn't the dancing itself. It was how <strong>natural</strong> it felt. No one was performing. No one was "good" or "bad." Movement was just another language they used to connect.</p>
      <p>Years later, at 21, I stumbled upon Argentine tango. It became my new garden. Through tango I grew emotionally, mentally, spiritually. I watched others transform too:</p>
      <div class="garden-pullquote">learning to trust, to listen, to embrace, to face themselves.</div>
      <p>Tango revealed that growth and connection are never solitary acts — they happen between us.</p>
      <p>When life brought me to Munich, I began to recreate that feeling. My living room became a small garden again — filled with plants, music, friends, laughter, and movement.</p>
      <p>Around a wooden table this time, we shared food, stories, and tango. Slowly, a community grew — not just of dancers, but of people who showed up for one another.</p>
      <p>Tango Garden is born from this journey — a place to grow on and off the dance floor. A space to connect deeply, to nurture yourself and others, to rediscover the joy of being present. Like every garden, it takes time, care, and warmth — but what blossoms is unforgettable.</p>
      <div class="garden-pullquote">❝We dance not just to move, but to belong.❞</div>
      <p>To find that rare space where we can breathe, feel, and grow together.</p>
      <p>I am glad that you came — and I am looking forward to meeting you in real life!</p>
      <p class="garden-sign-off">Hugs, Vangelis</p>
    </div>

    <div class="garden-story-images">
      <img src="/images/south.webp" alt="Crete, Summer 2020 — Dinner after a tango weekend" loading="lazy">
      <p class="garden-photo-caption">Crete, Summer 2020 — Last dinner after a long tango weekend full of warm embraces.</p>
      <img src="/images/miloga-de-archanes.webp" alt="Milonga de Archanes, Crete, Winter 2018" loading="lazy">
      <p class="garden-photo-caption">Crete, Winter 2018 — Dancing to Greek Tangos with traditional instruments.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Team banner -->
<section class="garden-team-banner" id="our-gardeners">
  <div>
    <h2>Our Gardeners</h2>
    <p>We're not performers. We're not tango purists.<br>We're people who believe connection matters more than perfection.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Team grid -->
<section class="garden-team-grid-section">
  <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
  <p class="garden-team-intro">Every person here has a story. Every person brings something unique to the garden.</p>

  <div class="garden-team-cards">
    <div class="garden-team-card">
      <span class="garden-team-badge">Cofounder</span>
      <img src="/images/vangelis.webp" alt="Vangelis Theodorakis" loading="lazy">
      <div class="garden-team-card-body">
        <h3>Vangelis Theodorakis</h3>
        <p class="garden-team-role">Lead Instructor</p>
        <p>Built Tango Garden after discovering his love for communities. Believes that tradition is the passing of the fire — not the worshipping of the ashes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="garden-team-card">
      <span class="garden-team-badge">Cofounder</span>
      <img src="/images/kristina.webp" alt="Kristina Yanushko" loading="lazy">
      <div class="garden-team-card-body">
        <h3>Kristina Yanushko</h3>
        <p class="garden-team-role">Lead Instructor</p>
        <p>Kristina focuses on helping students develop body awareness, confidence, and real connection — creating a space where people can grow both on and off the dance floor.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="garden-join">
    <h3>Want to Join the Team?</h3>
    <p>We're always looking for people who share our values and want to help grow the garden. If you've been dancing for a while and feel called to teach, let's talk.</p>
    <a href="https://wa.me/491602368723?text=Hi!%20I'm%20interested%20in%20joining%20the%20Tango%20Garden%20team." class="btn-primary">Join our team</a>
  </div>
</section>
`} />
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
.garden-hero {
      height: 100vh;
      min-height: 500px;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: url('/images/venue.webp') center/cover no-repeat;
    }
    .garden-hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: none;
    }
    .garden-hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 800px;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .garden-hero-content h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--green);
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .garden-scroll-hint {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      color: var(--green);
    }
    .garden-scroll-hint p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .garden-scroll-arrow {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      animation: gardenBounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
      display: block;
    }
    @keyframes gardenBounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(8px); }
    }

    /* Story section */
    .garden-story {
      background: var(--cream);
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .garden-story-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .garden-story-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .garden-story-text p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }
    .garden-pullquote {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--green);
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
      margin: 2rem 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .garden-sign-off {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--green);
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .garden-story-images img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      display: block;
    }
    .garden-story-images img + img { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .garden-photo-caption {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Gardeners banner */
    .garden-team-banner {
      min-height: 320px;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45,80,22,0.92), rgba(78,93,34,0.88));
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .garden-team-banner h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .garden-team-banner p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Team grid */
    .garden-team-grid-section {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .garden-team-grid-section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      color: var(--green);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .garden-team-intro {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .garden-team-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .garden-team-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
      position: relative;
    }
    .garden-team-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);
    }
    .garden-team-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      right: 12px;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .garden-team-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
      background: var(--cream);
    }
    .garden-team-card-body {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem 2rem;
    }
    .garden-team-card-body h3 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: var(--green);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }
    .garden-team-role {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }
    .garden-team-card-body p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-mid);
    }

    /* Join CTA */
    .garden-join {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      background: var(--cream);
      border-radius: 12px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .garden-join h3 {
      font-size: 1.65rem;
      color: var(--green);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .garden-join p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .garden-story-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .garden-story-images { order: -1; }
    }
</style>
